5.4 Army maintenance costs
==========================

Each army has a maintenance cost in money, metal, and/or jeweles, which
is for the salaries of the soldiers and upkeep of weapons and other
materials needed by the army.  The maintenance cost for each army is
given in the _army types_ table.  There is also a fixed per-army
overhead of 2000 sk.


