5.5 Movement points
===================

Your armies can move only a certain distance before they must stop and
rest.  How much they can move is expressed in the army's _move points_,
and the _move cost_ of the sectors they cross.

   For example, if an army has 13 move points, and it goes through
sectors with move costs of 4, 3, and 4, it will have two move points
left.  It will only be able to move onto a sector with move cost of two
or less.


