     This lists all spells you have cast which have not yet expired,
     and indicates how much longer the spell will last. For example,
     the _hide_sector_ spell lasts for eight thons, so would appear in
     the list until that time is up.  In this list you may [z]oom on a
     specific spell, which will give more detail, such as which sector
     the spell affects.  You may also [d]elete a spell which will
     terminate it early.

